{"inkVersion":21,"root":[["^PHONE: (TONE...)","\n","^PHONE: (CLICK)","\n","^SAM: (EXAGGERATED SIGH)","\n","^SAM: Dispatch Operator.","\n",["ev",{"^->":"0.8.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":"0.c-0","flg":2},{"s":["^Hey Sam, how's it going?",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"0.9.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":"0.c-1","flg":2},{"s":["^(Pretending not to hear her) Hello? Hellooooo?",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"0.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":"0.8.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n",{"->":"0.g-0"},{"#f":5}],"c-1":["ev",{"^->":"0.c-1.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":"0.9.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^SAM: Yeah, yeah. Funny. I could hang up on you and you won't get work for the day. See how you like that.","\n",[["ev",{"^->":"0.c-1.9.0.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":2},{"s":["^I'm sorry. I'm here. How are you?",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"0.c-1.9.1.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-1","flg":2},{"s":["^I'd just keep calling you. How's it goin' Sam?",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"0.c-1.9.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.0.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n",{"->":"0.g-0"},{"#f":5}],"c-1":["ev",{"^->":"0.c-1.9.c-1.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.1.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n",{"->":"0.g-0"},{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":5}],"g-0":["ev","str","^SAM","/str",1,{"x()":"SetCharacterState","exArgs":2},"pop","/ev","\n","^SAM: Oh, you know, the usual...?","\n","^SAM: Wait, not the usual. Coffee machine closest to *my* desk is broken. So now *I* have to walk all the way up to Logistics to get a fucking coffee now. Dez, I'm gonna do it this time. I'm gonna quit this shit job.","\n","^SAM: ...Maybe next week.","\n","^SAM: Anyway, I've got a fun one for you today.","\n",["ev",{"^->":"0.g-0.17.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-2","flg":2},{"s":["^Wait, really? A fun one?",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"0.g-0.18.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-3","flg":2},{"s":["^OK. Let's hear it.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-2":["ev",{"^->":"0.g-0.c-2.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.17.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^SAM: Nah. None of the jobs they give us are *fun*. Especially not this one.","\n",[["ev",{"^->":"0.g-0.c-2.9.0.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":2},{"s":["^Damn it. Well, let's hear it.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"0.g-0.c-2.9.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.0.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n",{"->":"0.g-1"},{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":5}],"c-3":["ev",{"^->":"0.g-0.c-3.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.18.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n",{"->":"0.g-1"},{"#f":5}],"#f":5}],"g-1":["^SAM: I got this report about the... Eastern Exchange Building.","\n","^SAM: I thought they had decommissioned that building but somehow it's still operating. Not like they would tell me anything actually important, but you know.","\n","^SAM: Says \"urgent\" on it but I'll be honest, they put that on almost every folder they send down here.","\n",["ev",{"^->":"0.g-1.6.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-4","flg":2},{"s":["^Bastards.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"0.g-1.7.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-5","flg":2},{"s":["^Maybe this time it's *really* urgent.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-4":["ev",{"^->":"0.g-1.c-4.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.6.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n",{"->":"0.g-2"},{"#f":5}],"c-5":["ev",{"^->":"0.g-1.c-5.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.7.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n",{"->":"0.g-2"},{"#f":5}],"#f":5}],"g-2":["^SAM: (LAUGHS) Yeah...","\n",["ev",{"^->":"0.g-2.2.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-6","flg":2},{"s":["^So what's the situation with the exchange building?",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-6":["ev",{"^->":"0.g-2.c-6.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.2.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n",{"->":"0.g-3"},{"#f":5}],"#f":5}],"g-3":["^SAM: The report says that the building's \"gone dark\". The Research team in there failed a critical handshake and someone needs to check in on them and restore communications with HQ.","\n",["ev",{"^->":"0.g-3.2.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-7","flg":2},{"s":["^And that someone is me?",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-7":["ev",{"^->":"0.g-3.c-7.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.2.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n",{"->":"0.g-4"},{"#f":5}],"#f":5}],"g-4":["^SAM: Correct. Lucky you! You get to meet with freaks from Research!","\n","^SAM: Of course it's fucking Research. They fuck up their duties and we're the ones who have to clean up after them.","\n",["ev",{"^->":"0.g-4.4.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-8","flg":2},{"s":["^Sam, I'm the one who's doing the clean up. You're just sitting at a desk.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"0.g-4.5.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-9","flg":2},{"s":["^Right. How will I... restore communications with HQ?",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-8":["ev",{"^->":"0.g-4.c-8.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.4.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^SAM: I thought we were a team?","\n",[["ev",{"^->":"0.g-4.c-8.9.0.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":2},{"s":["^We are. How will I restore communications with HQ?",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"0.g-4.c-8.9.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.0.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n",{"->":"0.g-5"},{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":5}],"c-9":["ev",{"^->":"0.g-4.c-9.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.5.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n",{"->":"0.g-5"},{"#f":5}],"#f":5}],"g-5":["^SAM: There's going to be a phone there, kinda like this one. That's the Universal Hotline. You'll have to figure out what's wrong with it and reconnect it.","\n",["ev",{"^->":"0.g-5.2.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-10","flg":2},{"s":["^That sounds easy.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"0.g-5.3.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-11","flg":2},{"s":["^That sounds like it's gonna be complicated.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-10":["ev",{"^->":"0.g-5.c-10.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.2.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^SAM: It's Metcom we're talking about. Nothing's ever easy here, Dez, and you know that.","\n",{"->":"0.g-6"},{"#f":5}],"c-11":["ev",{"^->":"0.g-5.c-11.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.3.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^SAM: Yup. Welcome to working at Metcom. Although you don't need me to tell you that.","\n",{"->":"0.g-6"},{"#f":5}],"#f":5}],"g-6":["^SAM: Do check that the Research team is alive and haven't all been, I don't know, eaten by giant bugs or whatever.","\n","^SAM: Gonna go now. Smoko.","\n",["ev",{"^->":"0.g-6.4.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-12","flg":2},{"s":["^Can you tell me what I need to do again? ",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"0.g-6.5.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-13","flg":2},{"s":["^Enjoy. Talk to you later.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-12":["ev",{"^->":"0.g-6.c-12.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.4.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^SAM: (SIGH) Yeah.","\n","^SAM: Go to the Eastern Exchange Building.","\n","^SAM: Check that the Research team is still alive.","\n","^SAM: Diagnose the problem with the Hotline, and find a way to fix it.","\n","^SAM: Restore communications with HQ, and ta-da! You're done.","\n","^SAM: Oh and call me when you're done. Obviously.","\n",[["ev",{"^->":"0.g-6.c-12.19.0.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":2},{"s":["^OK. Talk to you later.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"0.g-6.c-12.19.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.0.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n",{"->":"0.g-7"},{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":5}],"c-13":["ev",{"^->":"0.g-6.c-13.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.5.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n",{"->":"0.g-7"},{"#f":5}],"#f":5}],"g-7":["^PHONE: (CLICK)","\n","end",["done",{"#f":5,"#n":"g-8"}],{"#f":5}]}],"done",{"#f":1}],"listDefs":{}}